  <title>
    <phrase>The <quote>Preferences</quote> Command</phrase>
  </title>
  <indexterm>
    <primary>Preferences (command)</primary>
  </indexterm>
  <para>
    The <guimenuitem>File Preferences</guimenuitem> command displays the
    <link linkend="gimp-prefs-dialog">Preferences dialog</link>,
    which lets you alter a variety of settings that affect the look, feel,
    and performance of the <acronym>GIMP</acronym>.
  </para>
  <sect3>
    <title>
      <phrase>Activate Command</phrase>
    </title>
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para>
          You can access this command in the Toolbox menu bar through
          <menuchoice><guimenu><accel>F</accel>ile</guimenu><guimenuitem><accel>P</accel>references</guimenuitem></menuchoice>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </sect3>
</sect2>
